[[Doctor/Legends|Doctor]] '''Ephri Norz''' was a member of the [[New Republic Survey Corps/Legends|New Republic Survey Corps]] who held the rank of [[Colonel/Legends|colonel]].

Following the [[Battle of Dathomir (Hunt for Zsinj)|Battle of Dathomir]], Colonel Doctor Norz compiled reports on the sentient and animal life on [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]].

